            . I am clerk to the Solicitor of the Bank.</p>
               <p>Q. Was it with your knowledge that the last witness was employed to deal with the prisoner - A. It was.</p>
               <p>Q. Did the last witness come to you with two other witnesses, and give you these two notes - A. He did, on the 20th of July; I know Avory came with him, and I think Wainwright did; he had before communicated to me. The introduction he wrote on one of the notes bought of a stranger on the 20th of July, and his name 
               <persName id="t18131201-32-person396">
