                     <interp inst="t18131201-32-person401" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am one of the patrols of Bow-street office.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you make any agreement with Warman to detect any person dealing in bad bank notes - A. Yes, with Warman, by the order of Mr. Westwood. I agreed that Warman should detect some persons; I introduced Warman to Mr. Westwood I think on Monday, the 18th of July, or the 19th.</p>
               <p>Q. On Tuesday, the 20th of July, in consequence of any appointment with Warman did you go any where with Warman - A. I went to the Grange in Carey-street. 
               <persName id="t18131201-32-person402">
                  William 
                  Wainwright
               <interp inst="t18131201-32-person402" type="surname" value="Wainwright"></interp>
