                     <interp inst="t18131201-32-person403" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , is my hand writing. He said, he bought them of a man, he did not know his name; it was written bought of a stranger upon this one only; I believe it is my hand writing what is signed 
               <persName id="t18131201-32-person404">
                  Charles 
                  Warman
               <interp inst="t18131201-32-person404" type="surname" value="Warman"></interp>
