                  </persName>
            . Q. You are occasionally employed by the police office - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Were you in company with Avory on the 20th of July - A. Yes, at the Green Man public-house, Shire-lane. I went there for the purpose of assisting him in the detection of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you see the prisoner come there - A. No. I saw Avory mark a pound note, and gave it to 
               <persName id="t18131201-32-person410">
                  Charles 
